      <strong
      ><a href="https://github.com/Astrodevil/resource-gallery/issues"
      >Open Issue:</a
      ></strong
      > Improve the "Resource Gallery" and earn credits as early contributorðŸŽ‰
    </p>
    <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
      <Card
      href="/opensource"
      target="_blank"
      title="Open Source"
      body="Learn basics of open source with articles, videos and code resources."
      />
